{"title":"都市“包围”村庄","authors":["厉彦林"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":11,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"都市“包围”村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厉彦林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄很古老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无法考证生平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每片瓦都刻有朝代的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱村庄的都市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却只有几岁年纪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村包围城市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾是一代英杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改写中国历史的奇迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市返过头包围农村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是现代文明的自然手势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笋林状的高楼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织环绕乡村的篱笆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹影覆盖的茅舍扁着身子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守候唯一的秋塘碧水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垄垄金色的谷穗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被顺楼而下的打击乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震得摇晃不止"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农时季节被打乱步子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节日风俗，嫁女的花轿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被偷偷摄进镜头里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村人既坚守憩静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又跷脚探寻城里的秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡路是一根细短的扁担"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一头是乡村，一头是都市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着初识的两个世纪"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}